sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess

    Note over C,PA: LoadNavigationContext
    C->>A: LoadNavigationContext()
    A->>PM: LoadNavigationContext()
    PM->>PA: LoadNavigationContext()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(navigation_context.json)
    PA-->>PM: *NavigationContext (or nil)
    PM-->>A: *NavigationContext [defaults to {currentView:"okr"}]
    A-->>C: *NavigationContext (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,PA: SaveNavigationContext [NOT git-versioned]
    C->>A: SaveNavigationContext(ctx)
    A->>PM: SaveNavigationContext(managers.NavigationContext)
    PM->>PA: SaveNavigationContext(access.NavigationContext)
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(navigation_context.json) [no git commit]
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,PA: LoadTaskDrafts [NOT git-versioned]
    C->>A: LoadTaskDrafts()
    A->>PM: LoadTaskDrafts()
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskDrafts()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(tasks/drafts.json)
    PA-->>PM: json.RawMessage
    PM-->>A: json.RawMessage
    A-->>C: string (JSON)

    Note over C,PA: SaveTaskDrafts [NOT git-versioned]
    C->>A: SaveTaskDrafts(data)
    A->>PM: SaveTaskDrafts(json.RawMessage)
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskDrafts(json.RawMessage)
    PA->>PA: WriteFile(tasks/drafts.json)
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
